(I forgot about Bloodystrike! Now I have no reason for Gotron to be 
at the Pred group! Ah, I'll just say he wants to.)

Prebon

Prebon mumbled under his breath a secret message to Slayer. He hoped 
that to Ramulusit sounded like swearing.

"Hold your fire until I give the word. We might have to take a big 
battle instead of an assasination."

He looked at Ramulus.

"Striker is here. I will tell you where once you tell me why you 
brought anohte bot with you, and his name."
